From classic chocolate fudge to elegant red velvet, every bake is made to order. Share your event date, servings, and design inspiration— we’ll confirm availability and a pickup/delivery time window.

  • Lead time for custom cakes varies by design (typically 48–72 hours).
  • Delivery / pickup window shared at confirmation.
  • Payments via cash or local transfers on delivery.
